Thanks to Eve, I saved a great amount of money and time. I no longer need to shop every single day. The vacuum bags keep my food fresh for up to 10x longer.

I can clamp down all food on to all surfaces that are of large sizes and hard to store using only clips and rubber bands.

My problems were that I had fruits and vegetables in the fridge that, depending on the time of the year, went bad, but I can no longer buy organic fruits and vegetables in bulk and insert them in a Ziploc bag because it does not help much. The fruits then go bad the same day.

The other problem was already in use. I had a quality vacuum pump in my house, but I had problems with the sealing of the closure. I often encountered bought, sealed bags that would be undone just after closing the closure. I also encountered this problem of “not-100%-closed sealing” when I needed to replace it from time to time or switch from one product to the other.
